    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/f3b1104e6d923fa5e04d67cb0b8a0b8b.poster.avif?t=1759558560\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/f3b1104e6d923fa5e04d67cb0b8a0b8b.webm?t=1759558560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/f3b1104e6d923fa5e04d67cb0b8a0b8b.mp4?t=1759558560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宇宙的终结。人类已经消失，星星也熄灭了。然而，人类还是留下了一些东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >思想世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界中，一切都是相对的，而在伟大的虚空中，思想开始变得具象化。作为一个自我意识的思想之一，你努力实现思想世界的最终具象化，但这场战斗并不容易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/2fb22d5d5d344b4847cb512a78f89efd.poster.avif?t=1759558560\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/2fb22d5d5d344b4847cb512a78f89efd.webm?t=1759558560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/2fb22d5d5d344b4847cb512a78f89efd.mp4?t=1759558560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Tactics - 这是一款回合制战术类的地下城探险游戏。收集不同的生物到你的小队中，强化它们并将它们合并成更强大的生物，学习新的法术和找到强大的神器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集一支独特的生物小队，每个生物都有自己的优势和劣势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与深度战术战斗，地形对战斗产生影响。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将生物合并，创造更强大的生物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集各种法术，可以改变战斗的局势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找具有独特效果的“思想”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/e4673c700e59350c744c182cac2006f0.poster.avif?t=1759558560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/e4673c700e59350c744c182cac2006f0.webm?t=1759558560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/e4673c700e59350c744c182cac2006f0.mp4?t=1759558560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可重玩性高 - 过程生成和大量内容 使每次游戏都独一无二(200多个生物，120多种咒语，以及约300个‘想法’)。  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量可解锁的内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twitch 集成，允许与聊天进行互动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/a27a6c17a0503e0eac4299fad532a84e.poster.avif?t=1759558560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/a27a6c17a0503e0eac4299fad532a84e.webm?t=1759558560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345740/extras/a27a6c17a0503e0eac4299fad532a84e.mp4?t=1759558560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
